              "settings": {
                "html": "\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:3.75rem 3.75rem 7rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    \n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Unique Differentiator \u00b7 12 Months</span></div>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\">Ancient intelligence.<br>Modern evidence.</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:600px;margin:1.5rem 0 0;\">The only incubation track in North India dedicated to turning Ayurveda, herbal medicine, and traditional wellness knowledge into scientifically validated, commercially viable, globally competitive products \u2014 with rigorous evidence at the core.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#C49A2A;padding:4rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:3.75rem 3.75rem 7rem;\">\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2rem;text-align:center;\">\n      <div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">$200B+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.6);margin-top:4px;font-family:DM Mono;letter-spacing:0.05em;\">Global Herbal Market by 2030</div></div><div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">\u20b975,000 Cr</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.6);margin-top:4px;font-family:DM Mono;letter-spacing:0.05em;\">India's Ayush Sector</div></div><div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\"><1%</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.6);margin-top:4px;font-family:DM Mono;letter-spacing:0.05em;\">Ayurvedic Products Clinically Validated</div></div><div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">9,000+</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.6);margin-top:4px;font-family:DM Mono;letter-spacing:0.05em;\">Medicinal Plants Documented in India</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:3.75rem 3.75rem 7rem;\">\n\n    <!-- Opportunity -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">The Opportunity</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">A global market.<br><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">Almost no credible pipeline.</em></h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">The global market for herbal medicines, nutraceuticals, and traditional wellness products is approaching $200 billion. The demand has never been higher \u2014 in Europe, the US, Southeast Asia, and increasingly within India itself.</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">India has a head start no other country can replicate: 5,000 years of documented Ayurvedic knowledge, over 9,000 identified medicinal plants, and a Ministry of AYUSH with growing funding.</p>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:1.5rem;padding:1.5rem 2rem;border-left:3px solid #C49A2A;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;\">\n          <p style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">\"Less than 1% of Ayurvedic formulations in the market today have been validated through modern clinical standards. That's not a reason to dismiss Ayurveda \u2014 it's the <em style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-style:normal;\">size of the opportunity.</em>\"</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;\">\n        <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">$200B+</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Global Herbal Market</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Growing at 8\u201312% CAGR, driven by consumer demand for natural, evidence-backed wellness products</p></div><div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\u20b975,000 Cr</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">India's Ayush Sector</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Target of \u20b91.2 lakh crore by 2025 with government pushing hard on export promotion</p></div><div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">60+</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Countries with TM Policy</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Regulatory pathways for traditional medicine products are opening globally</p></div><div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\"><1%</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Products Validated</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">The gap between traditional knowledge and clinical evidence is the size of the opportunity</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Is this for you -->\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Is This For You?</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2713 This track is built for you if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're an Ayurveda practitioner (BAMS/MD) or traditional medicine researcher</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want to validate traditional formulations or develop herbal nutraceuticals</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You believe in the scientific rigor of evidence-based traditional medicine</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want to access AYUSH regulatory pathways and global markets</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#3B6D11;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You have a formulation, compound, or traditional practice worth validating scientifically</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1rem;\">\u2717 Consider a different track if\u2026</h3>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You want to sell traditional products without clinical validation</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">Your primary innovation is a medical device or digital health tool \u2014 apply for Medtech</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You already have a validated product with customers \u2014 consider the Accelerator</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;\"><span style=\"color:#A32D2D;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;\">\u2717</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#4A5C78;\">You're not open to subjecting traditional knowledge to modern scientific scrutiny</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA -->\n    <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:2rem;\">\n      <div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">Ready to apply for the Ayush track?</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0;\">8 seats. Rolling applications. Ancient knowledge deserves modern validation.</p></div>\n      <a href=\"/apply/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">Apply for This Track \u2192</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
              },
